00:00:11.206 --> 00:00:16.406 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Akari) [Heavy Breathing]</i>

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:21.373 position:24% line:83% align:start
Damn it. They just
keep coming.

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:24.139 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Akari) They're relentless!</i>

00:00:24.540 --> 00:00:27.840 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Heavy breathing]

00:00:27.873 --> 00:00:29.373 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:00:31.007 --> 00:00:34.073 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>We came all the way to Mars to</i>
 <i>save humanity,</i>

00:00:34.107 --> 00:00:39.008 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>only to find ourselves moments</i>
 <i>away from extermination by</i>
 <i>a swarm of mutant roaches.</i>

00:00:39.474 --> 00:00:42.674 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>Guess it's do or die,</i>
 <i>again.</i> Hmm.

00:00:43.474 --> 00:00:45.674 position:47% line:83% align:start
Are you seriously
laughing, Michelle?

00:00:45.707 --> 00:00:48.374 position:5% line:83% align:start
These dirty roaches don't
intimidate me.

00:00:48.407 --> 00:00:48.874 position:83% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:00:53.874 --> 00:00:55.774 position:30% line:89% align:start
(All) Joji-jo!

00:00:55.807 --> 00:00:58.407 position:5% line:89% align:start
Okay, are you ready Akari?

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:00.908 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yeah. Remember there's
a promise to keep.

00:01:02.774 --> 00:01:04.407 position:38% line:89% align:start
Promise?

00:01:06.140 --> 00:01:08.374 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Your promise that if we</i>
 <i>survive, we celebrate with a</i>
 <i>shower together!</i>

00:01:08.407 --> 00:01:09.974 position:30% line:89% align:start
No deal! Hmph!

00:01:12.407 --> 00:01:15.307 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's dangerous, but we need
another dose!

00:01:15.641 --> 00:01:17.974 position:7% line:83% align:start
I may just have to agree with
you on that one!

00:01:19.307 --> 00:01:21.774 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hmph. Time to finish this!

00:01:21.807 --> 00:01:22.707 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:01:25.541 --> 00:01:31.240 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:01:36.041 --> 00:01:43.308 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Screaming]

00:01:59.775 --> 00:02:03.408 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) Overpopulation has</i>
 <i>spawned a new human solution.</i>

00:02:03.441 --> 00:02:06.842 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) Moss and masses of</i>
 <i>cockroaches were sent to the</i>
 <i>red planet.</i>

00:02:06.875 --> 00:02:11.275 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) But six hundred years</i>
 <i>later, it all went terribly</i>
 <i>wrong.</i>

00:02:11.308 --> 00:02:16.475 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) The cockroaches</i>
 <i>evolved into aggressive bipedal</i>
 <i>colossi know as "terraformars."</i>

00:02:16.508 --> 00:02:25.308 position:13% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) And on Earth, a</i>
 <i>Martian disease with a 100%</i>
 <i>fatal alien engine virus wiped</i>
 <i>out entire communities.</i>

00:02:25.608 --> 00:02:29.642 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) To capture the</i>
 <i>hundred terraformar samples</i>
 <i>needed to create a vaccine,</i>

00:02:29.675 --> 00:02:34.808 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) volunteers across the</i>
 <i>world underwent a risky</i>
 <i>operation before being sent to</i>
 <i>Mars.</i>

00:02:48.910 --> 00:02:55.776 position:10% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) On this accursed,</i>
 <i>forsaken planet, against the</i>
 <i>odds, can humanity obtain</i>
 <i>their hope for tomorrow?</i>

00:04:36.076 --> 00:04:37.110 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) Michelle, come in!</i>

00:04:37.143 --> 00:04:38.076 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:04:39.143 --> 00:04:41.344 position:5% line:83% align:start
Coms re-established. Squads one
and two report in!

00:04:41.678 --> 00:04:43.578 position:21% line:89% align:start
Squads do you read?

00:04:43.611 --> 00:04:45.077 position:35% line:89% align:start
Report in!

00:04:45.111 --> 00:04:46.177 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:04:47.444 --> 00:04:49.545 position:5% line:77% align:start
Squad two reporting in. All
members are safe and accounted
for.

00:04:49.578 --> 00:04:56.044 position:13% line:71% align:start
We've been fighting since the
moment we landed! If I don't
get my beauty sleep, my skin's
gonna look awful!

00:04:58.378 --> 00:05:03.044 position:13% line:77% align:start
This is squad one. [Gasps]
Everyone here is alive, but
we're surrounded and...

00:05:03.077 --> 00:05:04.678 position:16% line:89% align:start
They're closing in fast!

00:05:04.711 --> 00:05:05.511 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) Wait what?!</i>

00:05:07.378 --> 00:05:09.444 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) We all have our hands</i>
 <i>full at the moment. You'll have</i>
 <i>to hold your own for now.</i>

00:05:09.478 --> 00:05:11.611 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Do what's necessary</i>
 <i>to survive!</i>

00:05:12.545 --> 00:05:14.444 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:05:14.478 --> 00:05:16.411 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Groaning]

00:05:18.244 --> 00:05:21.044 position:7% line:83% align:start
Remember to protect the serum,
at all costs!

00:05:21.278 --> 00:05:23.311 position:7% line:83% align:start
(Shokichi) Squad one, hang in
there!

00:05:23.344 --> 00:05:25.478 position:10% line:83% align:start
We're sending help your way,
now!

00:05:25.511 --> 00:05:27.478 position:16% line:89% align:start
Michelle, you two okay?

00:05:27.511 --> 00:05:31.645 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Yeah. And just a</i>
 <i>heads up, we've used a second</i>
 <i>dose.</i>

00:05:31.678 --> 00:05:34.678 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) Michelle! It's</i>
 <i>too dangerous!</i>

00:05:34.711 --> 00:05:38.678 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Grunts] Hell of a lot better
than being roach food!

00:05:40.344 --> 00:05:48.145 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Akari Hizamaru. He</i>
 <i>just keeps going. At times he</i>
 <i>seems unstoppable.</i>

00:05:49.212 --> 00:05:52.946 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Why? What drives you?</i>

00:05:53.546 --> 00:05:59.946 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Why do you keep</i>
 <i>fighting? The woman you loved is</i>
 <i>already gone.</i>

00:06:02.979 --> 00:06:06.345 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Yeah. Remember there's a</i>
 <i>promise to keep.</i>

00:06:06.612 --> 00:06:08.479 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Is that it?</i>

00:06:16.913 --> 00:06:18.312 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) Aww, how'd</i>
 <i>it break?</i>

00:06:18.946 --> 00:06:19.479 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:19.512 --> 00:06:20.612 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Chuckles]

00:06:21.612 --> 00:06:23.546 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) I'm really good</i>
 <i>at fixing stuff!</i>

00:06:24.412 --> 00:06:25.679 position:38% line:89% align:start
You are?

00:06:25.712 --> 00:06:27.279 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm staying over there
in that building.

00:06:28.013 --> 00:06:29.579 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) It'll give me</i>
 <i>something to do!</i>

00:06:29.946 --> 00:06:31.178 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh.

00:06:31.212 --> 00:06:33.212 position:27% line:5% align:start
 <i>The AE virus...</i>

00:06:33.245 --> 00:06:36.946 position:7% line:89% align:start
My name is Sakurato Harukaze.

00:06:46.112 --> 00:06:49.146 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) The boy infected with</i>
 <i>the AE virus.</i>

00:06:49.179 --> 00:06:52.213 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Remember there's a</i>
 <i>promise to keep.</i>

00:06:53.079 --> 00:06:55.079 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come to say your goodbyes?

00:06:55.113 --> 00:06:57.847 position:5% line:83% align:start
He's being quarantined
this afternoon.

00:06:58.113 --> 00:07:00.613 position:5% line:83% align:start
Try not to say anything that
will give the kid false hope.

00:07:00.647 --> 00:07:03.346 position:5% line:83% align:start
The mission to Mars
won't be easy.

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:08.813 position:5% line:71% align:start
Even if we manage to get enough
samples, there's no guarantee
the vaccine can even be made in
time.

00:07:09.046 --> 00:07:10.480 position:47% line:89% align:start
Yeah I know that.

00:07:13.980 --> 00:07:15.113 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) Here!</i>

00:07:15.947 --> 00:07:18.280 position:58% line:83% align:start
Whoa, it's as
good as new!

00:07:18.313 --> 00:07:19.179 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Chuckles]

00:07:19.213 --> 00:07:20.513 position:66% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:07:20.547 --> 00:07:22.014 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:07:22.046 --> 00:07:22.813 position:83% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:07:23.647 --> 00:07:25.813 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you really going
up there? To Mars?

00:07:26.446 --> 00:07:27.880 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:07:27.914 --> 00:07:30.480 position:13% line:83% align:start
So we probably won't see each
other again.

00:07:31.014 --> 00:07:32.213 position:5% line:89% align:start
Why do you say that?

00:07:32.246 --> 00:07:33.179 position:66% line:89% align:start
Because...

00:07:36.513 --> 00:07:38.847 position:35% line:83% align:start
Do you know why we're
going to Mars?

00:07:38.880 --> 00:07:41.346 position:35% line:83% align:start
We're going to find a
cure for your sickness.

00:07:41.380 --> 00:07:42.346 position:5% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:07:43.914 --> 00:07:47.046 position:24% line:77% align:start
It may seem like a small,
distant hope right now. But I
need you to fight.

00:07:47.346 --> 00:07:49.414 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Hold on to</i>
 <i>that for me.</i>

00:07:50.114 --> 00:07:52.147 position:16% line:89% align:start
So, you're coming back?

00:07:52.981 --> 00:07:54.781 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm promising you!

00:07:55.147 --> 00:07:56.848 position:35% line:89% align:start
You idiot.

00:07:59.548 --> 00:08:01.915 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Scoffs] Promises.

00:08:03.314 --> 00:08:04.381 position:38% line:5% align:start
 <i>Dammit.</i>

00:08:04.414 --> 00:08:05.648 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:08:05.681 --> 00:08:08.514 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Who do you think you</i>
 <i>are making a promise like that?</i>

00:08:08.548 --> 00:08:12.047 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>That second dose is a doozie.</i>

00:08:16.214 --> 00:08:20.347 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Grunts] Akari, wrap it up!
We're heading for squad one!

00:08:21.948 --> 00:08:23.881 position:69% line:89% align:start
[Screams]

00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:25.915 position:41% line:89% align:start
Akari!

00:08:28.447 --> 00:08:32.381 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:08:32.781 --> 00:08:34.047 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:08:34.848 --> 00:08:37.347 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:08:39.281 --> 00:08:41.781 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:08:42.247 --> 00:08:44.748 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>You're gonna have to try harder</i>
 <i>than that!</i>

00:08:47.915 --> 00:08:51.015 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hurry use the nets!
Create a barrier!

00:08:54.348 --> 00:08:55.849 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:08:55.882 --> 00:08:57.148 position:27% line:83% align:start
You idiot! What
are you doing?

00:08:57.181 --> 00:09:00.115 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm just trying to...Ah!

00:09:00.849 --> 00:09:01.782 position:75% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:09:01.815 --> 00:09:03.115 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yaeko!

00:09:04.415 --> 00:09:05.782 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:09:11.916 --> 00:09:14.715 position:30% line:5% align:start
 <i>[Groans] Dawn?</i>

00:09:16.148 --> 00:09:18.248 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:09:21.916 --> 00:09:25.115 position:10% line:83% align:start
So that's your plan? Letting
gravity do your dirty work?

00:09:25.148 --> 00:09:27.348 position:75% line:89% align:start
Jee Jo!

00:09:30.382 --> 00:09:32.215 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:09:58.049 --> 00:09:59.249 position:69% line:89% align:start
[Screams]

00:09:59.283 --> 00:10:00.049 position:5% line:89% align:start
Jo!

00:10:00.082 --> 00:10:01.917 position:69% line:89% align:start
[Screams]

00:10:01.950 --> 00:10:03.917 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:10:03.950 --> 00:10:04.917 position:80% line:89% align:start
Alex?

00:10:04.950 --> 00:10:06.983 position:5% line:89% align:start
Jeh-Jo!

00:10:08.883 --> 00:10:11.683 position:13% line:71% align:start
I hope you've learned your
lesson. Didn't you know major
league pitchers have an iron
grip?!

00:10:12.049 --> 00:10:13.616 position:80% line:89% align:start
Alex!

00:10:13.650 --> 00:10:15.650 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Groans]

00:10:16.017 --> 00:10:19.116 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:10:22.316 --> 00:10:25.049 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Whimpering] Huh?

00:10:28.283 --> 00:10:30.316 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:10:30.349 --> 00:10:33.850 position:7% line:83% align:start
Squad one reached. Casualties
high. Please report in.

00:10:34.650 --> 00:10:36.283 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) How are you holding</i>
 <i>up, Michelle?</i>

00:10:36.316 --> 00:10:38.583 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) The roaches!</i>
 <i>They got Akari!</i>

00:10:38.616 --> 00:10:39.750 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) What?</i>

00:10:39.783 --> 00:10:42.082 position:5% line:89% align:start
He doesn't have any serum left!

00:10:42.116 --> 00:10:43.716 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Shokichi) We're right behind</i>
 <i>you!</i>

00:10:44.182 --> 00:10:48.583 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>Akari, you understand, don't</i>
 <i>you? This burden we carry?</i>

00:10:49.082 --> 00:10:53.550 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) We're different from</i>
 <i>the others! We must never allow</i>
 <i>the roaches to capture our</i>
 <i>bodies!</i>

00:10:53.583 --> 00:10:59.584 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>The things they'd do...No! I</i>
 <i>won't let them. Just stay</i>
 <i>alive!  I'm on my way, Akari!</i>

00:11:02.984 --> 00:11:06.484 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>What...what happened?</i>

00:11:06.784 --> 00:11:09.450 position:33% line:5% align:start
 <i>Where am I?</i>

00:11:09.984 --> 00:11:12.450 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>Mars, that's right.</i>

00:11:15.117 --> 00:11:18.450 position:35% line:5% align:start
 <i>But...why?</i>

00:11:19.918 --> 00:11:23.784 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Sakurato, what's the</i>
 <i>first thing you want to eat when</i>
 <i>you get better?</i>

00:11:24.018 --> 00:11:26.018 position:44% line:89% align:start
Um.

00:11:26.050 --> 00:11:26.851 position:30% line:89% align:start
French fries!

00:11:26.884 --> 00:11:28.984 position:47% line:83% align:start
Done. Large order
of fries it is.

00:11:29.018 --> 00:11:32.851 position:5% line:83% align:start
Really? But my mom won't even
let me have a small.

00:11:32.884 --> 00:11:34.784 position:55% line:83% align:start
I'll get you a
triple XL.

00:11:34.817 --> 00:11:36.717 position:5% line:89% align:start
Let's not get carried away.

00:11:37.884 --> 00:11:40.918 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Akari...Is that why</i>
 <i>you fight?</i>

00:11:42.751 --> 00:11:44.083 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Anything else?</i>

00:11:44.117 --> 00:11:45.918 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:11:45.951 --> 00:11:48.117 position:16% line:89% align:start
I want to learn karate!

00:11:48.150 --> 00:11:49.384 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Chuckles]

00:11:56.450 --> 00:11:57.617 position:24% line:89% align:start
Now we're talking!

00:11:57.651 --> 00:11:58.885 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) I wanna</i>
 <i>see the ocean!</i>

00:11:58.919 --> 00:11:59.752 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:11:59.785 --> 00:12:00.885 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:12:00.919 --> 00:12:02.485 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:12:08.885 --> 00:12:10.151 position:24% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) You...</i>

00:12:11.518 --> 00:12:12.785 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Sakurato) And the zoo!</i>

00:12:12.818 --> 00:12:13.618 position:41% line:89% align:start
Sure!

00:12:13.652 --> 00:12:14.618 position:5% line:89% align:start
And then...

00:12:15.585 --> 00:12:16.985 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) He had the same virus</i>
 <i>as Yuriko.</i>

00:12:18.618 --> 00:12:20.852 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Yuriko) I want to</i>
 <i>eat some ramen.</i>

00:12:23.385 --> 00:12:24.919 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:12:25.652 --> 00:12:27.985 position:19% line:83% align:start
All right! I'll find us the
best ramen restaurant!

00:12:28.019 --> 00:12:29.718 position:5% line:89% align:start
And go snowboarding!

00:12:29.752 --> 00:12:30.818 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll buy the lift tickets!

00:12:30.852 --> 00:12:32.852 position:5% line:89% align:start
And have some beer.

00:12:32.885 --> 00:12:34.952 position:33% line:83% align:start
Sure thing. Just don't
drink too much!

00:12:34.985 --> 00:12:37.019 position:5% line:83% align:start
You can carry me
if I get drunk.

00:12:37.051 --> 00:12:39.318 position:47% line:83% align:start
[Chuckles] You're
hopeless, Yuriko.

00:12:40.485 --> 00:12:42.952 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Crying]

00:12:43.385 --> 00:12:46.518 position:5% line:89% align:start
And I want to go to Space Land.

00:12:47.485 --> 00:12:52.051 position:7% line:83% align:start
You sure about that? I've heard
space is pretty boring.

00:12:52.084 --> 00:12:55.051 position:5% line:89% align:start
And then...and then...

00:12:55.084 --> 00:12:56.752 position:38% line:89% align:start
Don't worry, Yuriko.

00:12:58.952 --> 00:13:03.352 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Akari) I found someone to do</i>
 <i>the surgery. I just have to make</i>
 <i>some extra money, and he'll fix</i>
 <i>you up.</i>

00:13:04.553 --> 00:13:06.719 position:5% line:83% align:start
You'll be yourself
in no time!

00:13:06.753 --> 00:13:08.586 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Crying]

