00:19:26.959 --> 00:19:29.392 position:5% line:83% align:start
I really hope Eva and the others
are safe.

00:19:29.425 --> 00:19:31.959 position:13% line:89% align:start
Um, was she in squad five?

00:19:31.992 --> 00:19:34.458 position:44% line:83% align:start
Mhm. She was going
to help me with something.

00:19:34.492 --> 00:19:35.091 position:44% line:89% align:start
