00:20:25.126 --> 00:20:29.693 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Now we just need</i>
 <i>to get home. After all,</i>
 <i>there's a promise to be kept.</i>

00:20:29.960 --> 00:20:32.426 position:7% line:89% align:start
