but losing Adolf would be
devastating strategically. His
power is unmatched.

00:21:22.761 --> 00:21:24.727 position:38% line:83% align:start
If they could find a
way to recover his-

00:21:24.761 --> 00:21:29.060 position:7% line:77% align:start
