now, is hope that everyone is
safe.

00:21:36.861 --> 00:21:43.060 position:13% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) We survived our</i>
 <i>second night on Mars with no</i>
 <i>roach sightings. What are they</i>
 <i>up to?</i>

00:21:44.327 --> 00:21:48.761 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(President Goodman) Now then. It</i>
 <i>appears that Plan Delta has been</i>
 <i>implemented.</i>

00:21:48.794 --> 00:21:52.127 position:16% line:5% align:start
Has the rescue ship been
deployed, President Snorresson?

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:57.661 position:5% line:5% align:start
Yes. In large part due to this
council's continual support
during these trying times.

00:21:58.127 --> 00:22:02.661 position:5% line:5% align:start
For too long we have tasked one
country to shoulder the burden
of this mission.

00:22:02.861 --> 00:22:04.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
But this is a battle for
humanity.

00:22:05.961 --> 00:22:10.794 position:7% line:5% align:start
We must contribute any and all
resources possible to ensure the
success of this mission.

00:22:42.261 --> 00:22:46.528 position:16% line:77% align:start
Don't worry, Michelle. We're
gonna make it home, just you
watch!

00:22:46.562 --> 00:22:47.929 position:66% line:89% align:start
