00:23:10.061 --> 00:23:11.828 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) That's the spirit! Let's</i>
 <i>stay cheerful!</i>

00:23:11.862 --> 00:23:17.228 position:10% line:77% align:start
